Description: Simulation and evaluation of multi-candidate district elections under various circumstances. Seat allocation under common allocation methods, vote share thresholds, and accounting for already allocated seats in multi-phase seat allocation (e.g., when allocation national seats to compensate for disproportionality in seats awarded in districts)
